      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match COU operating conditions within specified tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Bench measurements conducted at 37°C with porcine blood at physiological hematocrit (40±2%). Flow rates and rotational speeds match the 5 COU operating points within ±1.5% of target."
