      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD-predicted QoIs must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all validation points.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions agree within 8–12% of bench measurements across all operating points. Pressure-head predictions within 3.2% of FDA benchmark data. All comparisons pass the 15% acceptance threshold."
